@node History "DigiCam: History"

                                    History
                                   ---------
V1.61

   - changed: Made LED blinking while waiting before deletion of all frames in
              webcam mode.

V1.6

   - added:   @{" Webcam " link ActionsO} option. Turns your digital camera into a still webcamera.
              If you really want to do this, keep in mind that it is a 

   - changed: Found a good place to hide another ctrl-c check. DigiCam should
              be always breakable now.

   - changed: Download is speeded up 20% for the cost of a little more CPU usage

V1.5

   - added:   Image @{" upload " link UploadingO}.

   - added:   Support for newer cameras with @{" internal directory structure " link DirectoriesO}
              (DCF compliant cameras)

   - fixed:   The URL http://www.average.org/digicam/ was in wrong case and
              the page is on a case-sensitive server. Sorry.

   - changed: Erasing a range of frames is done in reverse order. The right
              frames will be deleted now.

   - changed: The date of saved files is set to the real camerainternal
              date of shooting now.

   - changed: Numbering of files is now done with fixed size number triples
              first is _001 aso.

V1.0

   - added: everything
@endnode

